                                                    The college has
                                                    launched a new
                                                    scheme for skill and
                                                    entrepreneurship
                                                    development of
                                                    students. We have
                                                    signed MoUs with
                                                    various government
                                                    agencies to conduct
                                                    job oriented add on
                                                    courses to the
                                                    students. The
                                                    agencies include
                                                    KELTRON, Centre for
                                                    Continuing Education
                                                    Kerala, ICT Academy
                                                    and Bharat Sevak
                                                    Samaj. After
                                                    completion of these
                                                    courses and the
                                                    subsequent
                                                    internships the
                                                    students will become
                                                    equipped with job
                                                    skills that help
                                                    them placed in good
                                                    companies

                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-md-9 row pt16">

                                                <div class="col-md-3 mb32 ">
                                                    <div class="faculties">
                                                        <div class="faculty_img">
                                                            <img src="/mes_college/static/img/faculty.jpg"
                                                                 class="w-100 h-100" loading="lazy" style=""/>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="faculty_name">
                                                            Dr. Faisal Babu
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="designation">Department of Arabic and Islamic
                                                            History
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-3 mb32 ">
                                                    <div class="faculties">
                                                        <div class="faculty_img">
                                                            <img src="/mes_college/static/img/faculty.jpg"
                                                                 class="w-100 h-100" loading="lazy" style=""/>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="faculty_name">
                                                            Shajitha M
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="designation">Department of Mathematics
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-3 mb32 ">
                                                    <div class="faculties">
                                                        <div class="faculty_img">
                                                            <img src="/mes_college/static/img/faculty.jpg"
                                                                 class="w-100 h-100" loading="lazy" style=""/>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="faculty_name">
                                                            Ratheesh CK
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="designation">Department of Malayalam
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </t>
                </t>
            </field>
        </record>
        <record id="skill_tune_page" model="website.page">
            <field name="url">/skill_tune</field>
            <field name="is_published">True</field>
            <field name="view_id" ref="skill_tune"/>
            <field name="track">True</field>
        </record>
    </data>
</odoo>